001package tv.freewheel.ad.interfaces;
002
003import java.util.HashMap;
004
005/**
006 * IEvent is the value object for carrying out event info:
007 */
008public interface IEvent {
009
010        /**
011         * Get the type of this event.
012         *
013         * @return type string, can be one of:
014         *              <br/>IConstants.EVENT_REQUEST_COMPLETE
015         *              <br/>IConstants.EVENT_REQUEST_CONTENT_VIDEO_PAUSE
016         *              <br/>IConstants.EVENT_REQUEST_CONTENT_VIDEO_RESUME
017         *              <br/>IConstants.EVENT_SLOT_ENDED
018         *              <br/>IConstants.EVENT_SLOT_STARTED
019         */
020        public String getType();
021        
022        /**
023         * Get the data information of this event.
024         *
025         * @return data as an HashMap<String, Object> Object
026         * 
027         * Note: the key of the data as following:
028         *              <br>
029         *              <br>IConstants.INFO_KEY_MESSAGE :all event will contain this
030         *              <br>IConstants.INFO_KEY_CUSTOM_ID :IConstants.EVENT_SLOT_ENDED/IConstants.EVENT_SLOT_STARTED will contain this
031         */
032        public HashMap<String, Object> getData();
033}
